      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>POTRUCH-Rosa. Of Rye, NY. Died June 9, 2000, at age 98. Mother of Miriam. Grandmother of Jessica, mother-in-law of Rabbi Robert Rothman. She was a brilliant scientist, a beautiful and elegant lady, multifaceted, multilingual, always charming and always interested in people. She will be missed. Marcia and Martin Levin</p>
